{"word":"πέταλον","slug":"πέταλον","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>πέταλον</b></el> <el>(πέτᾰλον, ου, τό,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:πετάννυμι'><el>πετάννυμι</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a leaf</i>, mostly in <a href='S:plural'>pl.</a>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>:— <a href='S:poetically'>poet.</a>, <el>νεικέων πέταλα</el> contentious votes (<a href='S:confer, compare'>cf.</a> <el>πεταλισμός</el>), <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>a leaf of metal</i>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}